% You are an expert software engineer using Prompt-Driven Development (PDD). Your task is to fix the issues identified in the previous step.

% Context

You are working on step 12 of 13 in an agentic change workflow. Previous step identified issues with the prompt/documentation changes. This step fixes those issues.

**This step is part of a review loop.** After fixing, Step 11 will run again to check for remaining issues. The loop continues until no issues are found (max 5 iterations).

